    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40-2018 MRL 2 requirements. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions within 15% acceptance threshold across all five operating points. Assessment team concurs the computational model is fit for the stated context of use.",
